{"tid":2174880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞球迷上街請願求挽留美斯","createTime":"2020-08-26T07:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:46:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c627117918ddd41bb792e4e2e4df2796dafc831","tid":2174880,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】美斯向巴塞隆拿提出離隊要求的消息傳出後，不少巴塞球迷隨即上街請願，盼球王留效。<br />\n<br />\n包括法新社在內多個媒體的消息指，阿根廷球王美斯（Lionel Messi）已告知巴塞隆拿會方，要求終止現時的合約。雙方都未證實相關消息，但巴塞球迷已急不及待作出反應，不少人在球會外聚集，要求會方留住美斯。<br />\n<br />\n有球迷叫囂，有人舉起美斯的波衫盼會方留住該阿根廷巨星，亦有人掛起寫上叫董事局成員滾蛋字句的橫額以示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n根據法新社披露，33歲的美斯已傳真告知巴塞，要求啟動合約內的解約條款，藉此自由身轉會。美斯現時合約直至2021年約滿，合約內原本列明今年夏天，擁有解約條款。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"d8402bf9ef4635dce2cf7cf97b2cdf9727f2c357","tid":2174880,"uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"熱刺球迷都走去奏熱鬧<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdThr3Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdThr3Y.png&h=7605e81a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e50ab2f24a071cf99c561d6dbf38523829a5404","tid":2174880,"uid":176282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d8402bf9ef4635dce2cf7cf97b2cdf9727f2c357","tid":2174880,"uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"熱刺球迷都走去奏熱鬧<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdThr3Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdThr3Y.png&h=7605e81a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"熱狗又玩分化"},{"pid":"a479b91a24f1375838c111f10f7acc6e8a9189eb","tid":2174880,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:34:36.000Z","msg":"失去了先懂珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76feacb71c3985b6e0711e9f9499ee78142161a","tid":2174880,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"加泰集會"},{